metadata.name: SHWDOBXO #1 Chrome Shine
metadata.description: SHWDOBXO are a collection of 111 "one-of-one" hand made 3D designs by @JeffJag from May 2021 to March 2022. The playfully misspelled 'Shadow Boxes' are series 2 of his 'Nobody Feels Time' 3D Art collections. The final token #111 is a community voted animated piece to be auctioned after 77% sold - each bidder receives a hand selected NFT cel (still) from the animation. After sell out there is a Token-gated Signed Print Store which will give each owner the ability to print one of three print quality levels (tbd) and have the "Physical Print" property updated on-chain so future collectors will know it exists.
